{
  "id": "5d50503257253a0017c421ae",
  "title": "解法メモ",
  "created": 1565544503,
  "updated": 1571286569,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5d50503257253a0017c421ae",
      "text": "解法メモ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544503,
      "updated": 1565544513
    },
    {
      "id": "5da7edfcaff09e0000d9a8af",
      "text": "　100人の囚人がいる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1571286525,
      "updated": 1571286537
    },
    {
      "id": "5da7ee09aff09e0000d9a8b0",
      "text": "　白か黒の帽子をかぶっている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1571286537,
      "updated": 1571286568
    },
    {
      "id": "5da7ee28aff09e0000d9a8b1",
      "text": "　",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1571286569,
      "updated": 1571286569
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505045aff09e00000ec655",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544518,
      "updated": 1565544518
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50511faff09e00000ec661",
      "text": " まず端から考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544736,
      "updated": 1565544737
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50511faff09e00000ec662",
      "text": " \t最初の1人について考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544736,
      "updated": 1565544737
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50511faff09e00000ec663",
      "text": " \t\t最初の1人は、何もヒントを得ることなく自分の帽子が黒か白かを答えなければいけない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544736,
      "updated": 1565544747
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50511faff09e00000ec664",
      "text": " \t\tどんなアルゴリズムでも彼の正解を保証することはできない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544736,
      "updated": 1565544737
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50511faff09e00000ec665",
      "text": " \tということは、残りの99人は全員正解する必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544736,
      "updated": 1565568975
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50511faff09e00000ec666",
      "text": " \t\tまず端から考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544736,
      "updated": 1565544737
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505123aff09e00000ec667",
      "text": " \t\t\t2人目は、1人目の発言を聞き、自分の前の98人の帽子を見ることで、自分の帽子の色がわかる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544740,
      "updated": 1565544813
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50516eaff09e00000ec668",
      "text": " \t\t\tどうすればこれが実現できるか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544814,
      "updated": 1565544876
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5051acaff09e00000ec669",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t例えば1人目が2人目の帽子の色を答えれば実現できる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544876,
      "updated": 1565544891
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5051bbaff09e00000ec66a",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\tじゃあこの方法で3人目はどうなるか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544891,
      "updated": 1565544927
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5051dfaff09e00000ec66c",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t3人目は「1人目が2人目の帽子の色を教え、2人目はその教わった色を答えた」という状態で自分の帽子の色を答えることになる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544927,
      "updated": 1565544957
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5051fdaff09e00000ec66d",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t\tヒントがないので正解を保証できない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544957,
      "updated": 1565545036
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5051ffaff09e00000ec66e",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t考察",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544960,
      "updated": 1565545117
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5052b3aff09e00000ec670",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t\t3人目「1人目と2人目は同じことを言ってるだけじゃないか！」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545139,
      "updated": 1565545150
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50529caff09e00000ec66f",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t\t1人目は2人目のためだけの情報ではなく3人目のための情報も伝える必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545117,
      "updated": 1565545157
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5052c5aff09e00000ec671",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t\t2人目は自分が正解するために、自分の理解した帽子の色を答える必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545157,
      "updated": 1565545191
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5052ecaff09e00000ec672",
      "text": " \t\t\tどうすればこれが実現できるか？take2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545196,
      "updated": 1565545208
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5052f8aff09e00000ec673",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t例えば",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545208,
      "updated": 1565545236
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505317aff09e00000ec674",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t1番目は2番目と3番目の帽子の色が同じ時に黒、異なる時に白と言う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545240,
      "updated": 1565545261
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50532daff09e00000ec675",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t2番目は(1番目の言った色、3番目の帽子の色)が",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545261,
      "updated": 1565545338
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50537aaff09e00000ec677",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t(黒, 黒)の時には黒と答える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545338,
      "updated": 1565545351
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505389aff09e00000ec678",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t(黒, 白)の時には白と答える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545354,
      "updated": 1565545364
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505398aff09e00000ec679",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t(白, 黒)の時には白と答える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545369,
      "updated": 1565545380
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505398aff09e00000ec67a",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t(白, 白)の時には黒と答える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545369,
      "updated": 1565545389
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5053afaff09e00000ec67b",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\tこれで正解できる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545391,
      "updated": 1565545395
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5053b1aff09e00000ec67c",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t3番目は、2番目の発言が正しいことを知っているので(1番目の言った色、2番目の言った色)が",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545394,
      "updated": 1565545512
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50541daff09e00000ec67f",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t(黒, 黒)の時には黒と答える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545501,
      "updated": 1565545501
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50541daff09e00000ec680",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t(黒, 白)の時には白と答える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545501,
      "updated": 1565545501
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50541daff09e00000ec681",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t(白, 黒)の時には白と答える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545501,
      "updated": 1565545501
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50541daff09e00000ec682",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t\t(白, 白)の時には黒と答える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545501,
      "updated": 1565545501
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505413aff09e00000ec67e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\tこれで正解できる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545491,
      "updated": 1565545522
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505431aff09e00000ec683",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t3人の時に確実に2人を救うアルゴリズムができた！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545522,
      "updated": 1565545544
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505447aff09e00000ec684",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tでは、どうすればこれを100人中99人を救うアルゴリズムにできるか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545544,
      "updated": 1565545573
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505575aff09e00000ec68c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t端から考えよう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545846,
      "updated": 1565545849
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505578aff09e00000ec68d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t4人中3人を救う方法を考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545849,
      "updated": 1565545862
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505465aff09e00000ec685",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t\t> 1人目は2人目のためだけの情報ではなく3人目のための情報も伝える必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545573,
      "updated": 1565545863
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5054edaff09e00000ec686",
      "text": "  \t\t   4人目の情報も伝える必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545710,
      "updated": 1565545868
    },
    {
      "id": "5d50550caff09e00000ec687",
      "text": "\t\t     ということは、4人目が黒か白かで1人目の回答は変わる必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545740,
      "updated": 1565545870
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505540aff09e00000ec68b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tさっきのこれも同じ性質だった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545793,
      "updated": 1565545988
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505603aff09e00000ec68e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t>1番目は2番目と3番目の帽子の色が同じ時に黒、異なる時に白と言う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545988,
      "updated": 1565545992
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505604aff09e00000ec68f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545989,
      "updated": 1565545995
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505513aff09e00000ec68a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565545747,
      "updated": 1565545747
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5050a7aff09e00000ec65c",
      "text": "「最大何人救うことができるか」よりも「99人を救うことが可能か」の方が簡単な問題。そして",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544615,
      "updated": 1565544663
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5050d7aff09e00000ec65e",
      "text": "「99人を救うことが可能か」と「99人救うことが可能だがそれはどうやるのか」は異質な問題。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544663,
      "updated": 1565544690
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5050f2aff09e00000ec65f",
      "text": "前者は可能かどうかの情報が求められているが、後者はその情報を与えられた上で、実現方法を考える問題だからだ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544692,
      "updated": 1565544720
    },
    {
      "id": "5d505110aff09e00000ec660",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544720,
      "updated": 1565544720
    },
    {
      "id": "5d5050a8aff09e00000ec65d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1565544616,
      "updated": 1565544616
    }
  ]
}